descriptionHtml:
if you wish for her to appear as in my screenies i used Fair skin Complexion with all the eye/makeup tweaks and Chrono's remodeled armors along with my preset on a cbbe body :3 (also she is pretty bad ass in game) 

CBBE Link http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?

Fair skin link by Hhaleyy http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?

Chrono's Remodeled armor link http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25259/?

This is Maya she is a Redguard Assassin Follower made with Vanilla assets she is totally dependent on whatever mods you have installed (skin eyes hair tex body ect) i have included the custom bodyslide preset i made when i made her i created her in Npc editor and if you use her feel free to upload screenies just keep them clean XD

She is found in the Sleeping giant inn in Riverwood
